{"tid":833594,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Dark Souls 3 黑暗靈魂3 The Fire Fades 薪火漸逝 [6]","createTime":"2018-09-23T15:28:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T11:35:41.000Z","uid":134640,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"5be4e0773515925150bed2d61ffb569cb875f088","tid":833594,"uid":134640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:28:59.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/29w7p1yq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F29w7p1yq&h=0fc3ecc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSteam:<br />\n<a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/374320/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F374320%2F&d=YiQ0ngMPxCLw3zTHWrzy78n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=535806de\" target=\"_blank\">http://store.steampowered.com/app/374320/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/506971/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F506971%2F&d=YiQ0ngMPxCLw3zTHWrzy78n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=9d92ac62\" target=\"_blank\">http://store.steampowered.com/app/506971/</a><br />\n買Season Pass=連所有DLC<br />\nDeluxe Edition=Game連DLC<br />\n<br />\n<strong>DARK SOULS III THE FIRE FADES EDITION</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/trpsoyf1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftrpsoyf1&h=95eb5ea8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n已推出<br />\n主機版GAME連DLC<br />\n<br />\nDLC2入口:初始火爐/DLC1修女營火<br />\n展示人性既牆:係湖到用疑態做粒黑色野(人性),再行埋去<br />\n<br />\n黑龍入口:第二個營火部lift中間有得碌出去,有個騎士石像係幻影<br />\n<br />\n黑龍NPC:唔可以去最尾張地圖,同埋要同長樓梯最上面個NPC講左野先<br />\n<br />\n希拉套衫:打完最尾BOSS,係營火向右行行到盡就有NPC殺,殺完就返去長樓梯最上面個位拎,向左行有個環印騎士殺左有圓盤<br />\n<br />\nDS1得PC,PS3,Xbox 360版<br />\nDS2原罪哲人版=連所有DLC+高清些少+遊戲內容有修改<br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n冇人開新post"},{"pid":"792f598518954f5263c97919d005c88c50e536b8","tid":833594,"uid":134640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:32:17.000